reviews.customers_say: Customers find the cardigan trendy and super soft, with a medium to heavy weight that keeps them warm without overheating.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable, stylish and I definitely recommend
items.body: I LOVE this. Found it from following an instagram influencer. That's typically not me at all, but I find myself having gained some weight very quickly and winter is coming and I needed to add to my wardrobe for when wearing PJs is unacceptable. I love this because I need more patterns in my wardrobe but it's honestly not that intense at all. I plan to pair it with black, white or gray shirts underneath, and likely with jeans. It's very soft, comfy and I think it's true to size. I prefer a looser fit but am a size 18, bought a XXL and think it fits perfectly. It's a decent thickness but doesn't seem like it will be too bulky or hot but it also isn't cheaply thin. Read more
items.author: anonymous98012

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Fall Layer, Comfy & Stylish!
items.body: So cute and comfy! I’ve only worn it once so far, but it exceeded my expectations. The material is soft and cozy without feeling too heavy, making it perfect for fall weather. I love that it can be dressed up with boots and jeans or kept casual with leggings. True to size and very versatile. I’m excited to wear it more this season! Read more
items.author: CoSGirl

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute Sweater
items.body: I really like this sweater. It is very soft. I like how it is longer in the back and shorter in the front and the unique pattern. The first few times washing though the fuzzy is a lot and I recommend washing separately. Read more
items.author: Bridgette B

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Motor sport
items.body: I am so in love with this sweater. I got alot of compliments on it. It is not to heavy or too light. It was 36 degrees this morning and 65 degrees this afternoon and I was totally comfortable in this sweater. I think I may order this in another color. It isnt itchy at all its very soft. Quality is good but I would watch out for snagging. Overall great purchase Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute!
items.body: This sweater fits me perfect. I am 5'0 and 105 lbs. The sleeves are on the shorter side so if you are taller it might not work as a long sleeve for you. Read more
items.author: Jesper Nielsen

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Perhaps I bought a size too large but it was super boxy on me….
items.body: cute sweater. Loved the pattern but it was like a potato sack on me. The length was great. Could wear with leggings or jeans so very versatile. Can not attest to durability as I did not keep it. Just a no for me. Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fall sweater!
items.body: Wonderful fall sweater, love the color. Thickness is perfect, nice and cozy tor fall, keeps you warm. Can wear with many different things, dress up or down…no smell. Read more

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Bad quality
items.body: This looked great out of the package and fit well but I wore it once after the return window and it's wearing and unraveling. Sad because I wasn't rough with it and I really loved it. You can tell in my picture the poor quality of craftsmanship and cheap yarn Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Red&green, Blue, Dark Khaki, White&pink, Black&white, Apricot, Coffee, Navy Blue, Red&yellow, Dark Green, Red, Khaki, Pink. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
